data.description: This renovated & restored mid century modern Berwick home has it all! Featuring 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths, an open floorpan, and a large entertaining area. The kitchen features quartz counters, with a butcher block island, SS appliances, gas stove, and built in pantry. The open concept dining and living room with vaulted ceilings and wood beams features a gas fireplace. The lower level has a living room, bedroom, and full bath. The upper level features four bedrooms, a full bath and a primary bedroom with en suite. The partially finished basement is currently used as a gym, the unfinished side provides ample storage space. The large fenced backyard has a large deck and fire pit area. Schedule your showing today!
